relation with the\naccreted stellar halo mass, as in observations. However, the accreted mass of\nbulges tends to correlate with their respective accreted stellar halo mass.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jul 2019 18:00:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-09-25"}
