ion\nand thus provides an embedding of $\\Re$ into $\\mathbb{F}[a,b,c]\\otimes\nU(\\mathfrak{sl}_2)$. We use the injection to show that $\\Re$ contains no zero\ndivisors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 3 Jul 2019 21:12:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-05"}
