 experiments, we find that the Tweets make a key contribution to the\npower of our approach. This finding informs future research not to unilaterally\npursue the domain-specific resource, but try to transform knowledge from the\nopen domain through ubiquitous signals such as emojis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jul 2019 03:38:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-05"}
