 band\nconsisting of four emission peaks (335, 359, 395, and 468 nm). The appearance\nof excitonic features in the absorption spectra of ZnS NPLs is explained by\ninterband electronic transitions, which is simulated in the framework of\ndensity functional theory (DFT). The presented simple and effective synthetic\nstrategy opens a new path to synthesize further NCs with shape and phase\ncontrol for advanced applications in electronics and photonics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jul 2019 12:29:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-05"}
