stance scales.\nQuasi-real photoproduction studies are also planned to search for additional\n$N^*$ states, the so-called hybrid baryons, for which the glue serves as an\nactive structural component. In this talk the $N^*$ programs from both CLAS and\nCLAS12 will be reviewed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 4 Jul 2019 14:01:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
